A visual comparison of a 6-bit/channel (18-bit) and 8-bit/channel (24-bit)

There are 8 rows of colors:

* 8-bit Red
* 6-bit Red

* 8-bit Green
* 6-bit Green

* 8-bit Blue
* 6-bit Blue

* 8-bit Gray
* 6-bit Gray

Does the top rows appear smooth and the bottom rows have Mach Banding?

Yes: Then your monitor is 8-bit/channel
No: Then your monitor is only displaying 6-bit/channel.  Upgrade to a real monitor.

